            Specification



Specification

     I have decided that the following criteria should be fulfilled when
designing the system:

- The game screen itself should update at 50Hz (the same rate as a
domestic PAL television set). This will mean the game will run smoothly,
and therefore appear as professional as possible.
- The inclusion of all the tile types specified in sections 1.2 and 1.3
- The limit to the number of levels in the game will only be the capacity
of the storage medium.
- The use of passwords and a high-score table.
- The introduction of time limits for bonus points
- The ability for anyone to easily edit the levels, and design their own.
- A range of new levels designed
- The overall aesthetic improvement over the original game
- The game should be suitable for distribution in the public domain
